# Official vendor architecture icons (AWS/GCP/Azure) — their usage terms
# permit using them to build diagrams but discourage redistributing the
# icon set itself, so these are downloaded locally rather than committed.
# See src/assets/icons/README.md for how to add them back.
src/assets/icons/aws-*.svg
src/assets/icons/gcp-*.svg
src/assets/icons/azure-*.svg
